{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6c2a18b2-7c0a-4f1f-9d4e-2c3a1b4d5e6f",
    "name": "Bus Split Payment Charged Flow",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": "End-to-end Chennai bus ticket flow where the Juspay order_status returns CHARGED with two txn_list entries (UPI + LOYALTYOS7) mirroring a real split-payment response. Verifies (a) the booking confirms with a usable ticket and (b) BOTH txn_list entries are persisted as payment_transaction rows by the txnList iteration in Lib.Payment.Domain.Action.orderStatusService."
  },
